citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:15 PM on
13-SEP-17.
After arriving at the property, the licensee stated that she was leaving soon and not going to be unavailable for an
inspection.
